{"featured_counts":1,"common_counts":38,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560507482/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=11\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560507482/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=9\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":16},"data":[{"id":566714208,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566714208","content":"\u003cp\u003e显然就是你不了解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最开始大家都以为是高中生，所以都很客气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后来发现这个人恐怕是一个高中学历的成年人民科……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e声称证明了哥德巴赫猜想的民科，简直不能更多，大佬们绝对见过不止一个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你说他错了，他说你不懂。你好心好意指点他，他直接开群嘲。你说他理论知识不足，他说你被官科洗脑。你批判他的论文，他说你官科欺压民科。看看他写的论文，满篇乱扯，想当然的给出低级公式，逻辑混乱，最该严谨的科学证明用一大片一大片比喻比拟修辞手法糊弄过去。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果这都去支持，那等于是侮辱全世界所有科研人员。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后再说点个人见解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使是高中生，从题目来看，题主想法也是相当有问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多半是本身实力不济，看到哥猜之后，妄想通过这种方式进清华。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就跟之前什么高考作文写甲骨文求保送的，也是花架子，剑走偏锋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真是的，耐下性子好好学习好好高考不好吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不打醒他，怕是真的要走上民科道路了。那就真的完了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545962862,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"dd0779ef0398be79527612f01c351233","url_token":"ceng-xi-wen-36","name":"曾玺文","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1570d58e5d2cacc